#CircuitBreakerSG D-39

Homey & comforting #dinner... Soya Sauce Braised Pork Belly with Beancurd Skin, Tau Pok & Egg.

Complete the meal with Sambal Kangkong & pickled Cucumber.

With extra rice 🍚 please!
.
.

@jessicacookinglog Definitely cook extra rice for this 😆
I will 2 bowls of rice for these😋😋
@myfoodiegallerysg Thanks dear. I love those beancurd skin 😍
Wow, love braise pork belly with beancurd skin. 😋💗💗
All-time dinner favourites Yvonne. The pork is tender, juicy and sauce is just flavourful.  Delicious! Yes I will ask for extra rice 😋😋
Lao Nuah 😋 for the first dish!
Wa I m drooling non stop, all my favourites! Remember boil more rice for me when I come 😆
@yvonnemsw first I must go out and buy the pork and I’ve become so lazy hahahahaha 😆
I really want to make this pork ... need to go buy Tau pok tomorrow
The first dish oh my God！Incredible looking! 😍
Mmmm this would go really well with my congee today!!! 😂
@bbblissball Taste even better the next day 😋
@in_frans_kitchen Yes... so homely, grow up eating this 😍
These dishes are so homely and perfect with a bowl of fluffy white rice! 😍😍
